data.description: Are you looking for a home in the low 200s? Well look no further, this lovely brick ranch has 3 bedrooms, 1 full bathroom, an attached 2 car garage & an oversized driveway! This home also features laminate flooring, a bonus room that could be used as a fourth bedroom or home office & a fenced in backyard! This beauty is waiting for you to make it your own, schedule your showing today!
